review_blob: Tried this beer after seeing the rave reviews here. This beer does not disappoint. Smells of dark chocolate, with expresso notes. Full bodied, almost a meal in a bottle, but is well balanced. Smooth.
Poured nice and dark with beige head. Aromas of chocolate, coffee, and slightly roasty. Tastes like it smells. A well balanced Porter, smooth and not too heavy.
